<li>[Deceased's name] will be deeply missed.</li>
<li> I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li>Sending you love and support.</li>
<li> Remembering [deceased's name]'s kindness and laughter.</li>
<li> May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>I'll always remember [deceased's name]'s warm smile.</li>
<li> I'm so sorry for your loss, my dear friend.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and sending strength.</li>
<li> Know that you're not alone in your grief.</li>
<li>I am deeply saddened by this news.</li>
<li> Your friendship means the world to me.</li>
<li> May peace surround you.</li>
